Title: Hand-painted wall tiles 'Ceramica Lignano ' ca .
Description:
Hand-painted wall tiles 'Ceramica Lignano' ca.1970. Very good condition, never used but quite dusty, needs to be cleaned.
These tiles are hand-painted; colour, shade and pattern may slightly vary from a tile to another.

Dimensions: 20 cm x 20 cm
Thickness: 8 mm

A few tiles may have very small chips. These tiles are hand-painted; colour, shade and pattern may slightly vary from a tile to another.
